{"tid":734390,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"肥通試手提「吹水機」 加冰水凍到似冷氣機","createTime":"2018-07-08T14:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T11:10:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aeab84cc819085090ca76146fb262612714952cd","tid":734390,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"肥通試手提「吹水機」 加冰水凍到似冷氣機<br />\n<br />\n最近社交媒體熱傳一部「手提冷氣機」，四四方方外形，的確非常可愛，但最實用之處，是百餘元的低廉價錢，還可以用尿袋作5V低電壓供電，竟能達致降低溫度效果，感覺非常節能。就此請教腦場Sales，他們為此機安了一個非常搞笑的名稱&mdash;&mdash;吹水機！話說此名同機身結構非常有關，因為它是以入水方式來調節溫度。<br />\n<br />\n《果籽》栽種品味，一籽了然。<br />\n<a href=\"http://as.appledaily.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fas.appledaily.com&d=9f6UbykoRrrOMhaUm3WEaS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=68726be0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fas.appledaily.com&h=4d6d975f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://as.appledaily.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NrEZYvg_KSI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNrEZYvg_KSI&d=9f6UbykoRrrOMhaUm3WEaS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e4d6f79c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NrEZYvg_KSI</a>"},{"pid":"32c188f3712b38b735f89c99550f3b60e3645b5c","tid":734390,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"開住個噴濕機用巴蕉吹咪重好 ?"},{"pid":"c4a9f16b7a9f54255d783859348341ace1ff6ca5","tid":734390,"uid":112606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"肥乜野通呀"},{"pid":"04faf730a51f1a7a1999fc550fefb51b35869dce","tid":734390,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"1a15a2e01f90d3a5a316fba987eb9f3939f03fdd","tid":734390,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04faf730a51f1a7a1999fc550fefb51b35869dce","tid":734390,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1